{{Qualification for championships (CONMEBOL)}}

The South American section of the '''[[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification]]''' acted as qualifiers for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]] to be held in Canada, Mexico, and the United States for national teams who are members of [[CONMEBOL]]. A total of 6 direct slots in the final tournament and 1 inter-confederation play-off slot were available for CONMEBOL teams.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/about-fifa/organisation/media-releases/bureau-of-the-council-recommends-slot-allocation-for-the-2026-fifa-wor-2878254|title=Bureau of the Council recommends slot allocation for the 2026 FIFA World Cup|publisher=FIFA|date=30 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/about-fifa/organisation/fifa-council/media-releases/fifa-council-prepares-congress-takes-key-decisions-for-the-future-of-t-2883353|title=FIFA Council prepares Congress, takes key decisions for the future of the FIFA World Cup|publisher=FIFA|date=9 May 2017}}</ref>

CONMEBOL was the first confederation to begin its qualification process for the 2026 FIFA World Cup, with [[#PAR v PER|Paraguay–Peru]] being the first match of the global qualification process.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/fifaplus/en/articles/road-to-world-cup-26-qualifiers-usa-canada-mexico|title=Road to the FIFA World Cup 26 set to begin|publisher=FIFA|date=28 August 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/tournaments/mens/worldcup/canadamexicousa2026/news/journey-to-historic-fifa-world-cup-2026-tm-kicks-off-in-south-america|title=CONMEBOL kick off journey of "great joy and happiness" to historic FIFA World Cup 2026™, says FIFA President|publisher=FIFA|date=7 September 2023}}</ref>

==Format==
On 22 August 2022, CONMEBOL sent a request to FIFA asking to keep the current qualification format that had been used since the 1998 World Cup qualification in South America.<ref>{{cite web|title=Conselho da Conmebol solicita à Fifa que mantenha formato atual das Eliminatórias para 2026|url=https://ge.globo.com/futebol/copa-do-mundo/eliminatorias-america-do-sul/noticia/2022/08/22/conselho-da-conmebol-solicita-a-fifa-que-mantenha-formato-atual-das-eliminatorias-para-2026.ghtml|language=pt|date=22 August 2022|publisher=globo.com|website=ge|access-date=23 August 2022|archive-date=23 August 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220823100439/https://ge.globo.com/futebol/copa-do-mundo/eliminatorias-america-do-sul/noticia/2022/08/22/conselho-da-conmebol-solicita-a-fifa-que-mantenha-formato-atual-das-eliminatorias-para-2026.ghtml|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=CONMEBOL's petition for the 2026 World Cup that could change FIFA's entire plans|url=https://bolavip.com/en/soccer/conmebol-petition-for-the-2026-world-cup-that-could-change-fifa-entire-plans-20220822-0039.html|date=22 August 2022|website=Bolavip|access-date=23 August 2022|archive-date=3 September 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220903205932/https://bolavip.com/en/soccer/conmebol-petition-for-the-2026-world-cup-that-could-change-fifa-entire-plans-20220822-0039.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Países sudamericanos pedirán a la FIFA mantener el formato de las Eliminatorias|url=https://www.conmebol.com/noticias/paises-sudamericanos-pediran-a-la-fifa-mantener-el-formato-de-las-eliminatorias/|language=es|date=22 August 2022|publisher=[[CONMEBOL]]|access-date=23 August 2022|archive-date=3 September 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220903055033/https://www.conmebol.com/noticias/paises-sudamericanos-pediran-a-la-fifa-mantener-el-formato-de-las-eliminatorias/|url-status=live}}</ref> This was confirmed, with the first games of the qualifiers tentatively to be played in March or June 2023.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bolavip.com/pe/seleccionperuana/Seleccion-Peruana-se-confirmo-fecha-y-formato-Eliminatorias-Sudamericanas-2026-mundial--20221001-0010.html|title=Conmebol confirmó fecha para el inicio de las Eliminatorias 2026|language=es|date=4 October 2022|website=Bolavip|access-date=12 December 2022|archive-date=16 October 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221016102441/https://bolavip.com/pe/seleccionperuana/Seleccion-Peruana-se-confirmo-fecha-y-formato-Eliminatorias-Sudamericanas-2026-mundial--20221001-0010.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ecuavisa.com/deportes/futbol-internacional/eliminatorias-conmebol-iniciarian-en-junio-del-2023-primera-fecha-fifa-seria-en-marzo-EX3909503|title=Eliminatorias Conmebol iniciarían en junio del 2023; primera fecha FIFA sería en marzo|publisher=[[Ecuavisa]]|last=Verdezoto|first=Kevin|date=8 December 2022|access-date=22 March 2023|language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.futbolred.com/selecciones-nacionales/eliminatorias-conmebol-2026-comenzarian-en-junio-2023-fechas-fifa-de-marzo-serian-para-amistosos-173305|title=Eliminatorias 2026: ¿cuándo arranca la clasificatoria sudamericana?|publisher=Futbolred|date=28 December 2022|access-date=22 March 2023|language=es}}</ref>

On 27 February 2023, CONMEBOL president [[Alejandro Domínguez (football executive)|Alejandro Domínguez]] announced that the qualifiers would start in September 2023,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ole.com.ar/ecuador/internacional/inicio-eliminatorias-sudamericanas-alejandro-domingez-conmebol_0_7jduA0XaIm.html|title=Eliminatorias Sudamericanas iniciarán entre septiembre y octubre|publisher=[[Olé (sports newspaper)|Olé]]|date=27 February 2023|access-date=22 March 2023|language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.directvsports.com/futbol/Alejandro-Dominguez-confirmo-que-las-Eliminatorias-comenzaran-en-septiembre-20230227-0046.html|title=Alejandro Domínguez confirmó que las Eliminatorias comenzarán en septiembre|publisher=Directv Sports|date=27 February 2023|access-date=22 March 2023|language=es}}</ref> which was ratified by the CONMEBOL Council in the run-up to the 73rd [[FIFA Congress]] held on 16 March in [[Kigali]], [[Rwanda]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dobleamarilla.com.ar/america/el-consejo-de-conmebol-aprobo-por-unanimidad-el-inicio-de-las-eliminatorias-en-septiembre_a6411aeca0874bfa4779c8ce6|title=El Consejo de Conmebol aprobó por unanimidad el inicio de las Eliminatorias en septiembre|publisher=Doble Amarilla|date=15 March 2023|access-date=22 March 2023|language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.americatv.com.pe/deportes/futbol-mundial/conmebol-definio-calendario-eliminatorias-rumbo-al-mundial-2026-n434827|title=Conmebol definió el calendario para las Eliminatorias rumbo al Mundial 2026|publisher=[[América Televisión]]|date=15 March 2023|access-date=22 March 2023|language=es}}</ref>

The qualification structure remained the same as in previous editions (despite the increase of slots available to CONMEBOL teams), wherein each team played each other team twice in a home-and-away [[Round-robin tournament|round-robin]] format.<ref name="match schedule">{{cite web|url=https://www.conmebol.com/noticias/el-calendario-de-partidos-para-las-eliminatorias-sudamericanas/|title=El calendario de partidos para las Eliminatorias Sudamericanas|publisher=[[CONMEBOL]]|date=22 March 2023|access-date=22 March 2023|language=es}}</ref>

Prior to the commencement of the qualification competition, [[Ecuador national football team|Ecuador]] were deducted 3 points for the use of a document containing false information for [[Byron Castillo]] in the [[2022 FIFA World Cup qualification (CONMEBOL)|previous]] World Cup qualification cycle.<ref name="ecuador_deduction1">{{cite web |url=https://www.tas-cas.org/fileadmin/user_upload/CAS_Media_Release_9175_9176_Decision.pdf |title=The CAS confirms the eligibility of the player Byron Castillo (Ecuador) but imposes sanctions against the Ecuadorian Football Federation for a violation of the FIFA regulations |work=Court of Arbitration for Sport |date=8 November 2022 |access-date=12 December 2022 |archive-date=3 December 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221203052908/https://www.tas-cas.org/fileadmin/user_upload/CAS_Media_Release_9175_9176_Decision.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>

==Schedule==
The qualifying matches were held on a total of 18 matchdays on dates that fall within the [[FIFA International Match Calendar]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://digitalhub.fifa.com/m/3123d37097318f7f/original/Men-s-International-Match-Calendar-2023-2030_EN.pdf|title=Men's International Match Calendar 2023-2030|publisher=FIFA|access-date=14 September 2023|date=4 April 2023}}</ref> The match schedule was same that was used in the [[2022 FIFA World Cup qualification (CONMEBOL)|previous edition]] of the competition. Six matchdays were played in each of 2023, 2024, and 2025.<ref name="match schedule"/>

